title: Cant make Pixel II call from Tesla Model 3
content:
Error message "The number or code you have dialed is incorrect. Please check the number and try again....Error Message 7, Switch 386" . 
Whenever I am in or near my new Tesla Model 3, i get this message, when dialing ON the phone or on the Tesla screen. CRAZY that I can not make a phone call from my new car. Please help! - did not match any answers in Pixel Phone Help.
